				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I think I read someone say he had trouble finding the rod in Qeynos sewers. It is in the shark pool on the lower level, at loc +650 +50 (By the way, after killing 5 sharks I finally got that doll, and the collar you get in return is not too bad: armor 3, +5 HP). The sharks are level 15-17. I think you can get the rod without killing them and get out of water if youre quick to click on the rod and swim back, lol !<BR>
I created a newbie Dark Elf to scout the resting place of IZAH. Did you notice that when you are INSIDE the Blind Fish Inn, through the underwater window you can see the rod, and you can actually grab it from inside by clicking on it through the window ? lol !<BR>

